query {
  ~version: 
}

docs {
  ## List Good Received Notes by Vendor
  แสดงรายการใบรับสินค้าทั้งหมดของผู้ขายรายหนึ่งพร้อมการแบ่งหน้าและตัวกรอง ใช้สำหรับตรวจสอบประวัติการส่งมอบของผู้ขาย

  Lists all goods receiving records for a specific vendor with pagination and filtering. Used to review a vendor's delivery history and track performance metrics.

  ### Path Parameters
  | Name | Type | Description |
  |------|------|-------------|
  | `bu_code` | string | Business unit code |
  | `vendor_id` | string (UUID) | Vendor ID |

  ### Query Parameters
  | Name | Type | Required | Default | Description |
  |------|------|----------|---------|-------------|
  | `page` | number | No | 1 | Page number |
  | `perpage` | number | No | 10 | Items per page |
  | `version` | string | No | latest | API version |

  ### Headers
  | Name | Required | Description |
  |------|----------|-------------|
  | `Authorization` | Yes | `Bearer {{access_token}}` |
  | `x-app-id` | Yes | `{{x_app_id}}` |

  ### Permissions
  - **Permission key**: `procurement.goods_received_note:view`
  - **Roles**: HOD, Purchase, Approval

  ### Sample Response
  ```json
  {
    "data": [
      {
        "id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c4d",
        "grn_no": "GRN-2026-0042",
        "grn_date": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z",
        "doc_status": "committed",
        "invoice_no": "INV-2026-0100",
        "vendor_name": "ABC Supplies Co., Ltd.",
        "currency_code": "THB",
        "net_amount": 10000.00,
        "total_amount": 10700.00,
        "created_at": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z"
      }
    ],
    "paginate": {
      "page": 1,
      "perpage": 10,
      "pages": 3,
      "total": 28,
      "prev": null,
      "next": 2
    },
    "status": 200,
    "success": true,
    "message": "Success",
    "timestamp": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z"
  }
  ```

  ### Error Responses
  | Status | When |
  |--------|------|
  | 401 | Missing or invalid bearer token |
  | 403 | User lacks `procurement.goods_received_note:view` permission |
  | 404 | Vendor not found |

  > Service-layer errors propagate via TCP; see micro-business for full list.
}

